A blockchain is a database that store information and allow automation. Everything that is recorded in the blockchain is public, accessible and immutable. The informtion are stored in blocks and, when those blocks are filled, another one is added consequently. (from here the name block chain). 
A smart contract is simple program that allow automation. the automations should be coded in from a developer. The automation that a smart contract allows are depending on the needs of the writer, from a transaction of crypto currencies to workflow automation.
A script is a text that describe and enable a function. A trasaction is a function that transfer cryptocurrencies. the transaction change data on the block chain and can cost money. 
